Class Statement

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.tugraz.ist.soma.statements.Statement
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Assignment, ElseStatement, ForLoop, IfStatement, VariableDeclaration, WhileLoop

    public abstract class Statement
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a statement. It is the base class for Assignment, VariableDeclaration, IfStatement, ElseStatement, ForLoop and WhileLoop.
